Better Reddit Check 

Based on the Reddit Check extension by Hrishikesh Bakshi. Receive instant
visual feedback whether any URL has been submitted to Reddit. If the page
you're on has been submitted, you can open a new tab to join the
discussion, or you can resubmit the link. If the link hasn't been
submitted, you can start a new submission right from the Chrome toolbar.

It is distributed under the GNU General Public License - see the
accompanying LICENSE file for more details.
 
This extension was modified/created by  paulburton0 [at] gmail.com
 
Extension install link:
https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/bnikifloagjncfjbniboapgdehnlemmd
